examples.en: The dog's tail began to wag excitedly.
They had wagged it from school.
Some wag had drawn a face on the wall.
examples.ru: Какой-то шутник нарисовал на стене рожицу.

examples.en: He wagged his head back and forth.
The happy dog wagged his tail.
Bind them fast to their chairs that they shall not wag.
examples.ru: Привяжи их крепко к стульям, чтобы они не смогли пошевелиться.

examples.en: She wagged her finger at the children as she scolded them.
examples.ru: Отчитывая детей, она грозила им пальцем.
